查看用户权限：
show grants for wylte@localhost; 
授权：
grant all on `sys`.`wylte` from 'wylte'@'%';
GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, REFERENCES, DELETE, CREATE, DROP, ALTER, INDEX, CREATE VIEW, SHOW VIEW 
ON `wylte`.* TO 'wylte'@'%';
取消授权：
revoke all on `sys`.`wylte` from 'wylte'@'%';

